change_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ID"               AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ObjectID"         AS "ObjectID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."Time"             AS "Time",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."Attribute"        AS "Attribute",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."OldValue"         AS "OldValue",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."NewValue"         AS "NewValue",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"        AS "ChangedBy",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."OperationID"      AS "OperationID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."OperationType"    AS "OperationType",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"    AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "c_o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
        ON "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ObjectID" = "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"
WHERE "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentCategory" IN ('Standard PO')

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"                                                           AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreatedBy_ID"                                                 AS "CreatedBy",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Header_ID"                                                    AS "Header",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Material_ID"                                                  AS "Material",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."RequestedBy_ID"                                               AS "RequestedBy",
	"PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreationExecutionType"                                        AS "CreationExecutionType",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreationTime"                                                 AS "CreationTime",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ChangeDate"                                                   AS "ChangeDate",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Currency"                                                     AS "Currency",
	"PurchaseDocumentLine"."NetAmount"                                                    AS "NetAmount",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."NetUnitPrice"                                                 AS "NetUnitPrice",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentType"                                                 AS "DocumentType",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Quantity"                                                     AS "Quantity",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."QuantityUnit"                                                 AS "QuantityUnit",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Description"                                                  AS "Description",
	"PurchaseDocumentLine"."LineNumber"										              AS "LineNumber",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."PurchaseDocumentNumber"                                       AS "PurchaseDocumentNumber",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."IsCanceled"                                                   AS "IsCanceled",
	"PurchaseDocumentLine"."IsGoodsReceiptRequired"										  AS "IsGoodsReceiptRequired",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentCategory"										      AS "DocumentCategory",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."SourceSystemInstance"	                                      AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine"  AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
WHERE "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentCategory" IN ('Standard PO')
